Dagannoth spawn are baby dagannoth hatched from eggs found near the walls or water of Waterbirth Dungeon. The eggs will hatch as players walk nearby, and they will attack the player with melee. Also, two dagannoth spawn will attack the player as they walk through the barricades to the ladder on sublevel 1.
